https://cassandra.apache.org/doc/latest/data_modeling/intro.html

Apache Cassandra Documentation v4.0-beta3

RMDBS
- object domain driven: table_person, table_property
- normalization: join when query data from separated tables
- centralized storage
- primary key, index key
- relational integrity: foriegn key constraint

cassandra
- query driven: table_view_person_property
- denormalization: same data duplicated across multiple tables
- partition: across multiple storage nodes
- primary key: (partition key, clustering key)
  - consistent hashing: func(partition key) -> partitions
- queries invlove single table

Data Model Analysis

- partition size
- data redundancy
- disk space
- lightweight transaction (LWT)

### Denormalization

- performance
- business requirement: ex. enclosed historical snapshot

### Query-first design

- domain object -> table
- query -> table

